{"tid":2178933,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"環球時報：希望「航母殺手」導彈永無機會在南海使用","createTime":"2020-08-28T17:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T21:50:33.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4518129ab69e39210eb0f086e3f16db5dec8aa10","tid":2178933,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T17:52:44.000Z","msg":"環球時報發表社評，表示希望解放軍被稱為「航母殺手」的東風-21D及東風-26B導彈，永無機會在南海使用。社評認為，如果僅僅是在南海自由航行且無害通過，美國軍艦無需關注解放軍的任何演習，但是美國出沒在南海的軍艦，都有潛在的來者不善，如果美國航母有在南海向解放軍發起攻擊的預案，那麼屆時這兩款導彈就是為那些航母所準備。社評又指，解放軍決不會在南海上打第一槍，但是第二槍說不定就是東風-21D和東風-26B。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546612-20200829.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546612-20200829.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyKb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=76c92f49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546612-20200829.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4496fc5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546612-20200829.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"17d8e6e9a2814601f749f615e0fe8cb0f842665c","tid":2178933,"uid":261796,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T17:53:43.000Z","msg":"俾人炸左咪用唔到囉"},{"pid":"c8a123f9988a87ee3b88dc85f674977c530ec863","tid":2178933,"uid":58738,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T17:59:37.000Z","msg":"B1，B2轟炸機群表示明白"},{"pid":"147b2017606b276dd06ea1fedc20980481978260","tid":2178933,"uid":6030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T18:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6XVTmBG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6XVTmBG.png&h=c4ba6927&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3af877c79e33c7f99584c0be83aece57f4a2e3db","tid":2178933,"uid":227271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T18:0